<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA54">
<l>arava maṭalvēḻa māṉkuruntam puḷvāy</l>
<l>kuravai kuṭamulaimaṟ kuṉṟaṅ – karaviṉṟi</l>
<l>viṭṭiṟuttu mēyttocittuk kīṇṭukōt tāṭiyuṇ</l>
<l>ṭaṭṭeṭutta ceṅka ṇavaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, without hiding, sent the snake , broke the murderous bull elephant,</l>
<l>grazed the cows, broke the wild lime tree, tore the bird’s beak, linked [hands]</l>
<l>in the Kuravai dance, danced with the pots,   drank from the breast [of the demoness],</l> 
<l>killed the wrestlers [and] lifted the hill, is him with red eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
